:: Head's Office Refusal
<<set $outside to 0>><<set $location to "school">><<schooleffects>><<effects>>
<<set _offeredclothing to ($clothingselector is "m" ? "남자 교복" : "여자 교복")>>
<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
	"그-그치만 이건 _offeredclothing 인데요." 당신이 말한다.
<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
	"_offeredclothing을 입진 않을거야!" 당신이 말한다.
<<else>>
	<<if $player.sex is $clothingselector and !$backgroundTraits.includes("crossdresser")>><!-- Crossdresser trait makes PC distressed by not crossdressing and so goes to "I can't" -->
		"<<print ($clothingselector is "f" ? "바지" : "치마")>>가 하나도 없는 거 확실해요?" 당신이 묻는다.
	<<else>>
		"그래도 _offeredclothing을 입을 순 없어요!" 당신이 말한다.
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>
<<if ($player.gender_appearance is $clothingselector) and !$genderknown.includes("Leighton") and !playerChastity("hidden")>> <!-- Leighton didn't expect this and checks the PC's records for their sex -->
	그는 잠깐 동안 약간 혼란스러워 하다가, 다시 컴퓨터로 돌아가 무언가를 찾는다. 그는 대략 훑어보다가
		<<if $player.penisExist and $player.vaginaExist>><!-- implication: PC's ambiguous sex is recorded as medical information -->
			무언가 발견하곤 숨을 들이킨다.
		<<elseif $backgroundTraits.includes("crossdresser")>><!-- deliberately ambiguous implication: PC has been crossdressing for long enough for it to be on file -->
			무언가 발견하곤 조소한다.
		<<else>>
			무언가 발견하곤 이맛살을 찌푸리며 타이핑한다.
		<</if>>
		그가 다시 고개를 들어 말한다. "미안하지만, 그 옷이 지금 여기 있는 전부야. 그러니, 이제 옷을 입어."
	<<set $genderknown.pushUnique("Leighton")>><<if $player.penisExist and $player.vaginaExist>><<detention -1>><</if>> <!-- Leighton is too surprised to be angry at herm PC right now -->
<<elseif $player.sex is $clothingselector and $genderknown.includes("Leighton")>>
	그는 당신을 근엄하게 쳐다보며 비웃는다. "네가 <<print ($clothingselector is "m" ? "여자아이" : "남자아이")>>처럼 입고 싶다면, 그건 네 할 탓이긴 하지만, 아마 다음부터 그렇게 입고 다녀야 할 거다. 지금은, 그 옷을 입어."
<<else>>
	그는 근엄하게 쳐다본다. "말대답 하지마. 내가 옷 갈아입으라 했으면 어서 갈아입어."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<link [[옷을 갈아입고 나온다 (0:01)|Hallways]]>><<schoolspareclothes>><<pass 1>><<endevent>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[나온다|Hallways]]>><<detention 3>><<endevent>><</link>><<gdelinquency>>
<br>

:: School Passout
<<sydneySchedule>>
<<if isPregnancyEnding()>>
	<<pregnancyPassout "school">>
<<elseif _sydney_location is "library" and (C.npc.Sydney.init isnot 1 or ($sydneySeen and !$sydneySeen.includes("libRescue")) or $rng gte 21)>>
	<<pass 1 hour>>
	당신은 잠시 정신을 잃고 있었다. 당신은 짧은 헉 소리를 들었고, 다시 미끄러져 정신을 잃기 전에 당신이 일으켜 세워지는 듯한 느낌을 받는다.
	<br><br>
	<<trauma 6>><<set $stress -= 2000>>
	<<link [[다음|Sydney Library Rescue]]>><</link>>
<<else>>
	<<unset $passoutReason>>
	<<pass 1 hour>>
	당신은 잠시 정신을 잃고 있었다.
	<br><br>

	<<if dangerEvent()>>
		<<if Time.schoolDay and $schoolstate isnot "early" and $schoolstate isnot "late">>
			<<if $rng gte 81 and $settings.analEnabled and !playerChastity("anus")>>
				<<link [[다음|School Passout Exhibit]]>><<upperruined>><<lowerruined>><<underruined>><</link>>
			<<elseif $rng gte 1>>
				<<link [[다음|School Passout Rape]]>><<set $molestationstart to 1>><</link>>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<if $rng gte 51>>
				<<link [[다음|School Passout Gang Rape]]>><<set $molestationstart to 1>><</link>>
			<<elseif $rng gte 1>>
				<<link [[다음|School Passout Gang Rape]]>><<set $molestationstart to 1>><</link>>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
		<<trauma 6>><<set $stress -= 2000>>
	<<else>>
		<<if C.npc.Kylar.rage gte 96 and C.npc.Kylar.state is "active">>
			<<link [[일어난다|Kylar Basement]]>><<pass 1 hour>><</link>>
			<br>
		<<elseif Time.schoolDay and $schoolstate isnot "early" and $schoolstate isnot "late">>
			<<link [[다음|School Passout Infirmary]]>><</link>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<ambulance>>
		<</if>>
		<<trauma 6>><<set $stress -= 2000>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

