<br>
<<link [[징계 면제|Head's Office No Detention]]>><</link>>
<br>
<<if $schoolfameboard isnot 1 and $schoolfameblackmail isnot undefined>>
	<<link [[사진 촬영은 그만|Head's Office No Photoshoots]]>><</link>>
	<br>

	<<if hasSexStat("exhibitionism", 4)>>
		<<link [[사진 촬영할 때마다 대가 요구|Head's Office Pay Photoshoots]]>><</link>><<exhibitionist4>>
